Build what?

41
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:05,290
I'll cook instead.

42
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:09,400
Because I'm a cook.

43
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:13,390
Geez. Oh, no...

44
00:03:16,720 --> 00:03:18,540
Well,

45
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:20,990
