46
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:23,220
Don't get angry and listen.

47
00:03:28,540 --> 00:03:30,550
All done. Let's go.

48
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:37,200
Why is she in a bad mood?
Why are you giving me a stink eye?

49
